'''Subrat Saurabh''' is an Indian writer, poet and blogger from [[Bengaluru]]. He launched his book titled ''Kuch Woh Pal'', a collection of Hindi poems, in October 2017.<ref>{{citation |title=The Booknerds Hangout launches book |url=https://www.dailypioneer.com/2017/state-editions/the-booknerds-hangout-launches-book.html |work=[[The Pioneer (newspaper)|The Pioneer]] |agency=PNS  |location=[[Dehradun]] |date=31 October 2017 }}</ref> Some of his tweets were covered in media posts.<ref>{{citation |title=Watch: Twitter can’t stop gushing over this toddler doing Shah Rukh Khan’s signature move |url=https://www.indiatvnews.com/buzz/news-watch-twitter-can-t-stop-gushing-over-this-toddler-doing-shah-rukh-khan-s-signature-move-454117 |work=[[India TV]] |agency=India TV Buzz Desk  |location=[[New Delhi]] |date=23 July 2018 }}</ref><ref>{{citation |title=These funny memes of ‘Sanju’ movie will make you ROFL; check them out |url=http://www.freepressjournal.in/entertainment/these-funny-memes-of-sanju-movie-will-make-you-rofl-check-them-out/1310844 |work=[[The Free Press Journal]] |agency=FPJ Web Desk |date=5 July 2018 }}</ref><ref>{{citation |last=Bhatt |first=Priyanka |title=While Numbers Kept Fluctuating, Rahul Gandhi Was Brutally Trolled For Karnataka Poll Results |url=https://www.indiatimes.com/news/india/while-numbers-kept-fluctuating-rahul-gandhi-was-brutally-trolled-for-karnataka-poll-results-345451.html |work=[[India Times]] |date=15 May 2018 }}</ref> He launched another book 'And We Walked Away' in 2018.

==Life==
Saurabh is from [[Muzaffarpur]], [[Bihar]]. He is an engineer by profession and works as a software consultant with a firm in [[Bengaluru]].<ref>{{citation |last=Varshney |first=Tarun |title=Interview with Subrat Saurabh - Author of Kuch Wo Pal |url=http://www.tarunvarshney.com/2017/09/author-interview-subrat-saurabh-kuch-woh-pal.html |work=tarunvarshney.com |year=2017 }}</ref>

