* ''Kuch Woh Pal'' (2017)
* And We Walked Away (2018)<ref>{{citation |last=Sharma |first=Aryan |title=This young writer said that passion for writing is the solution to my all problems |url=https://m.patrika.com/jaipur-news/interaction-with-writer-subrat-saurabh-3422834/ |work=[[Rajasthan Patrika]] |date=17 September 2018 |location=[[Jaipur]] }}</ref><ref>{{citation |title=Author Subrat Saurabh in Jaipur on Sunday with 'And We Walked Away' |url=http://m.sanjeevnitoday.com/state/othar-subrata-saurabh-with-and-we-walked-away-in-jaipur-on-sunday/20180915/168976 |work=[[Sanjeevni Today]] |date=15 September 2018 }}</ref><ref>{{citation |title=Will make a career in writing staying in India after touring 12 countries: Subrat Saurabh |url=http://m.sanjeevnitoday.com/editorial/career-india-will-stay-after-12-countries-after-touring-subrata-saurabh/20180916/169108 |work=[[Sanjeevni Today]] |date=16 September 2018 }}</ref><ref>{{citation |title=Expressoul |url=http://epaper.newindianexpress.com/m5/1840699/The-New-Indian-Express-Bengaluru/03-OCT-2018#page/20/1 |work=[[The New Indian Express]] |date=3 October 2018 }}</ref>

